longBusinessSummary: Seshasayee Paper and Boards Limited engages in the manufacture and sale of printing and writing paper in India. The company owns and operates integrated pulp, paper, and paper board mills. The company exports its products. Seshasayee Paper and Boards Limited was incorporated in 1960 and is based in Erode, India.
